description: We are pleased to introduce the Condos at 126 D Street, a new construction, 5-unit development near the Washington Village Development and steps to the Broadway T station. Unit #1 is a spacious bi-level unit with two bedrooms, two baths, a home office, and a large patio yard off the living room. The high-end finishes include hardwood floors, a working kitchen with white shaker cabinets, waterfall Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and Marble bathrooms. A garage bay with two-car parking is included! It's the last unit available - two have closed, and two units are UA!
